- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 The EmberMUD help system can teach you about different commands you 
 can use, give you information about different skills and spells you 
 may get, etc.  Here is a partial list of help subjects, grouped by  
 relevance.  If you don't understand something in the MUD, try the   
